Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:03.69,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna뉴궁서m\fs80\bord8\frx352\fry20\frz9.471\pos(865,195)\c&H796070&\3c&HFFEFEF&}고토
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}우울한 월요일이\N찾아오고야 말았다...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,감기 나아서\N다행이네!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 응...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 언니는 학교 며칠이나\N빠질 수 있었으니까
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,감기 걸린 게\N더 나았어?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,하나도 안 좋은데~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,왜애~?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,항상 쉬고 싶다고\N그러잖아...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,학교 가는 건\N싫지만
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,나 같은 인간은\N하루 빠지는 것만으로도
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,반 애들한테서\N존재가 까맣게 잊혀진단다~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,흐응...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,언니는 진짜\N더럽게 성가시구나~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,아!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,엄마가\N밥 다 됐대~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}예, 그렇답니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}언니도 스스로가\N성가시고 또 성가셔서
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아주 터져\N죽어버릴 것 같은―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}응?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그래도\N잠깐 있어봐?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}밴드 뛰면서
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}라이브 하우스에서\N알바까지 하고 있는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:01:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\fna두리둥실}나는 이미 아싸를\N탈출해버렸던 게 아닌지!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.93,0:01:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}좋았어!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}한 번 더\N기타 들고 가자!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그러면 분명\N누군가 말 걸어주겠지~?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}넵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그렇게 남에게 기대기만 하는데\N누가 말 걸어줄 리가 없겠지~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:12.51,Default - A,,0,0,0,,있잖아
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:14.13,Default - A,,0,0,0,,저번 음스테 봤어?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:15.63,Default - A,,0,0,0,,아, 봤지 봤지~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,신곡 구독\N해금됐었더라~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,「BAKWIMPS」!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,이젠 진짜~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,어제부터\N너무 돌려 들어서
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,안 듣고 있어도\N노래가 들려온다니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,헐, 대박~!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs100}밴드 이야기!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn양재백두체b\fs90\bord6\fscy70\t(00,100,\fscx200\fscy200)\t(100,200,\fscx80\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscx130\fscy130)}듸악!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,10)\fna두리둥실\fs90\bord5\fscy70\t(00,100,\fscy150)\t(100,200,\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscy100)\pos(1269.333,713.334)}힉!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,10)\fna두리둥실\fs90\bord5\fscy70\t(00,100,\fscy150)\t(100,200,\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscy100)\frz343.9\pos(466.666,649.334)}힉!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,우와...!\N고토 씨, 무슨 일이야?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨가 말 걸어오다니\N별일이네~!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.60,0:01:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}항상 누가 먼저 말 걸어주는 걸\N전제로 깔고 있다 보니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}대화를\N시작하는 법을~!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(0,1040,\fscx95\fscy95)}엑, 아으악...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,까먹었어요...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1920,1080)\t(1350,1710,\clip(0,0,0,1080))}-그 잠깐 동안!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:41.78,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fna두리둥실\fs150\bord10\move(3400,845,-1500,845,0,1000)}점심시간이야!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}차라리\N이래서 다행이었을 거야...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}만일 제대로 대화가\N이어졌다면 지금 쯤...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\pos(480,980)}에~?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\pos(480,980)}느닷없이\N대화에 끼어든다 했더니
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur5\pos(480,980)}우리가 하는 얘기를\N엿듣고 있었던 거예요~?
