Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,흑, 우욱...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,잊고프다아...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,에, 대단하다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,키..키타 씨!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,어느새...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,갑자기 도망치길래\N무슨 일인가 했더니
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,와, 감동이다~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨,\N기타 잘 쳤구나!
