Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,방금 전 연주!\N엄청 빠져든다고 할지!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}자..잔뜩 칭찬해주네!?\N좋은 사람이다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,밴드라도 하는 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,일단은, 네...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fn양재매화체s\fs80\bord6\fscy30\t(00,150,\fscy200)\t(250,520,\fscy80)\t(520,620,\fscy100)\frz342.6\pos(1500,295)\c&H448CED&\3c&H3A30D2&}키따~앙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,있지!\N또 뭐 칠 줄 알아?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,쳐줄래?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이..인싸 오라가 너무 눈부셔서\N직시할 수가 없다~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,그 전에 아까는\N무슨 볼일 있어서 왔던 거 아냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이..이것은\N가입 권유 찬스!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,지금 저희 밴드의\N기타 & 뽀컬을 찾고 있어서...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 저기...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,그게...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,키타 씨는\N기타 칠 줄 안다길래...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,아아...\N그랬구나...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어, 어라??
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,미안해, 고토 씨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,나, 그 밴드에는\N들어갈 수 없어...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아니...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 그게...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,710)}저는 칙칙하지만\N다른 멤버들은 명랑해서요!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(980,710)}아니, 고토 씨가\N싫다는 게 아니라...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(980,710)}주말에는\N다 같이 바베큐!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(980,710)}반 년에 한 번 있는\N구기 대회!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(980,710)}라이브 뒷풀이는\N리무진에서 하는데다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1110,720)}행사도 아주\N푸짐하게 많아서어!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1110,720)}그 정도로 파티에 미친\N밴드는 싫은데...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 저기...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,또 뭐냐아~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,그게...\N솔직하게 말하면 나...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,기타 전혀 못 치거든
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,전에 잠깐 있던\N밴드도 말야...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,선배랑 친해지려고 칠 수 있다면서\N거짓말하고 들어간 거라고 할지...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,그래도 결국...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,정말 1도 모르겠어서\N도망쳐버렸거든...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,하나도...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,응...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:08:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,기타는 여기를 짜라란\N하기만 하는 게 아니구나~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,어...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,이 나무 봉은\N장식인 줄 알았지 뭐야~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,초심자가 혼자 시작하기에는\N너무 어렵더라구~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,메이저 코드?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,마이너?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,무슨 야구 얘기인 줄~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}모른다는 차원이\N그냥 아예 다른데...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨는 기타,\N누구한테 배운 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아..아니\N거의 독학으로...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,어어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,정말!?\N대단하다!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,아니이...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,전혀...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,우, 우헿…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,흐헿?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,으헤헤헿헤…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna두리둥실\fs50\bord5\frz333.4\pos(1350,865)}히히힣헿ㅎ헿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,10)\fna두리둥실\fs90\bord5\fscy70\t(00,100,\fscy150)\t(100,200,\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscy100)\pos(1350,865)\frz333.4}으휋!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,맞다!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨,\N기타 가르쳐주면 안 돼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,내 선생님이 돼줘!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,이렇게 잘 치는\N고토 씨가 가르쳐준다면
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,열심히 해보자는\N기분이 들 것 같은데!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}아..아니이~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:35.09,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,이번에야말로\N제대로 기타 칠 줄 알게 돼서!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,저번 밴드 선배들한테\N사과하러 가고 싶어!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,있지!\N언제 가르쳐줄 수 있을까!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,방과 후라든가!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,아아...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,제가 방과 후에는\N라이브 하우스에서
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,알바를...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,600)\fna두리둥실\fs50\bord4\fscy70\t(00,100,\fscy150)\t(100,200,\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscy100)\pos(745,395)}으!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 알바 끝난 다음이라도\N괜찮으니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,근처에\N스튜디오 같은 건 없어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,거기서 제발!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:59.27,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,400)\fna두리둥실\fs\frz6.66\pos(830.334,518)}아..알게써여...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:59.27,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,400)\fna두리둥실\fs\frz352\pos(1217,483.333)}정말!?\N고마워~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나는 바~보니~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}거절을 하란 마랴아아~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘 바로 가도 돼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 예, 옙...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}망했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs80}망했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs85}망했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs90}망했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&\fs100}망했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}니지카쨩네한테 클럽족같은\N느낌으로 위장해달라고 해야지~!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,응?
