Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,게다가 거기 멤버 선배들이\N여기서 살았는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}그랬군요...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,잠깐!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨가 뒤에 서면\N길을 알 수가 없잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,죄송해요...\N이 거리는 아직 낯설어서...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,으어어, 창피해애...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,이러는 게\N더 창피하다니까~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 조금만\N더 가면 돼서...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,장소는\N스태리란 곳이에요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,거기에 니지카쨩이랑\N료 씨가 이미 와 있을...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs100}뭐!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:56.45,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,10)\fna두리둥실\fs90\bord5\pos(1280,795)}욱…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.36,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,800)\fna두리둥실\fs70\bord5\pos(1185,450)}응??
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,미안해...\N나 역시 돌아가볼래...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,어??
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,왜...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,붋…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,미안...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,이유는 말 못하지만\N거기에는 도저히 못 가겠어!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,여기에 왔단 건\N절대 그 사람들한테는
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,말하지 말―!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs100}오!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨔아앙~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,잘은 모르겠지만\N에너드링 잔뜩 사 왔당~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,근데...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\fad(00,800)\bord6}탈주한 기타아아아!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,탈주.. 기타...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,키타쨩...!\N왜 여기에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,아읏, 아읏...\N제..제가...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,어라?
