Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮아!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,대강 알겠으니까\N고토 씨는 이만 쉬어!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,우쭐대서\N죄송함미다...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,다행이다!\N큰일나진 않아서~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}가..감사합니...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어라...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이 손가락...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨는...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,왜 밴드를 시작하려고\N생각하게 된 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:14:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,인도어 취미인 주제에\N화려하고 멋진데다...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,인기도\N끌 수 있으니깐...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}동기가\N전부 너무 불순해~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,아...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,세계평화...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,세계평화를\N전하고 싶어서...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,목표가\N참 고상하구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.75,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\fs60\bord0\pos(885,915)\c&H4E594C&}티켓 판매는 {\c&H2C6673&}17:00부터 {\c&H4E594C&}시작합니다.
